overline.description: Overline text (text with a line above it) is one of the smallest font sizes. It's used to introduce a headline.

caption.description: Caption is one of the smallest font sizes. It's used sparingly to annotate imagery.

default.description: A primary color is the color displayed most frequently across our app's screens and components. The primary color can be used to make a color theme for your app, including dark and light primary color variants.

primary.description: Used as the container surface on top of the application.

tertiary.description: Used on top of container surface. Could be used to section content.

overlay.description: used as an overlay on top of a surface.

brand.description: Roboto has a dual nature. It has a mechanical skeleton and the forms are largely geometric. At the same time, the font features friendly and open curves.
